snippet.title: QuadSmash arcade game for XBLIG and PC - Launch trailer
snippet.description:
QuadSmash is a frantic couch-multiplayer arcade game available on Xbox Live Indie Games and PC.

Visit http://www.quadsmash.com/ to get a demo, screenshots and more!
